These are Puzzles for 2x3 Level 4

.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-4-1::.
City: venice, hamburg, paris
The people perfer 3 different movie-genres: fantasy, animation, mystery
1. the person traveling to venice is in an even position##4
2. the person watching fantasy movies is on the left or right of the person watching mystery movies##3
3. the person watching fantasy movies is the person traveling to hamburg##1
4. the person traveling to paris is on the far left##1
5. the person watching animation movies is the person watching animation movies##1

.:: Answer ::.
|        |      1      |      2      |     3     |
| City   | paris | venice | hamburg |
| Movie-Genre    | animation    | mystery | fantasy |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-4-2::.
City: london, nizza, edinburgh
There are 3 different favourite beverages: 7up, mirinda, soy-milk
1. the person traveling to london is on the far right##1
2. the person drinking mirinda is in an even position##4
3. the person drinking soy-milk is on the left of the person traveling to edinburgh##1
4. the person drinking mirinda is the person drinking mirinda##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |    1    |     2      |      3      |
| City       | nizza | edinburgh | london |
| Beverage   | soy-milk    | mirinda     | 7up        |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-4-3::.
City: prague, new-york, nizza
There are 3 different nationalities: thai, nigerian, brazilian
1. the person traveling to prague is on the right of the thai##1
2. the nigerian is on the left of the thai##1
3. the person traveling to new-york is in an even position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |      2      |   3    |
| City         | nizza     | new-york | prague |
| Nationality   | nigerian | thai     | brazilian  |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-4-4::.
City: hannover, edinburgh, prague
The people prefer 3 different music-genres: hip-hop, funk, country
1. the person traveling to edinburgh is the fan of funk##1
2. the person traveling to hannover is the fan of country##1
3. the person traveling to edinburgh is in an even position##4
4. the person traveling to edinburgh is on the right of the person traveling to prague##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |    2    |    3     |
| City   | prague | edinburgh  | hannover  |
| Music-Genre         | hip-hop  | funk | country |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-4-5::.
The people prefer 3 different music-genres: house, hip-hop, dubstep
The people perfer 3 different movie-genres: action, documentary, romance
1. the fan of dubstep is between the fan of house and the person watching action movies##2
2. the fan of hip-hop is in an odd position##4
3. the person watching romance movies is on the left of the person watching action movies##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |     2     |    3     |
| Music-Genre         | house   | dubstep | hip-hop    |
| Movie-Genre   | documentary | romance     | action |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-4-6::.
3 different brands of cigars are smoked: alhambra, prince, swisher
City: rome, liverpool, miami
1. the alhambra-smoker is the person traveling to liverpool##1
2. the person traveling to miami is the prince-smoker##1
3. the prince-smoker is in an odd position##4
4. the swisher-smoker is on the right of the person traveling to miami##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |     1      |     2      |    3     |
| Cigar   | prince | swisher | alhambra   |
| City   | miami     | rome    | liverpool |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-4-7::.
The people grow 3 different varities of flowers: bellflower, iris, amaryllis
There are 3 different favourite colors: amber, blood-red, mauve
1. the person who growsiris is on the right of the person who growsbellflower##1
2. the person who growsbellflower is between the person who likes mauve and the person who growsamaryllis##2
3. the person who growsbellflower is on the left of the person who growsiris##1
4. the person who likes amber is in an even position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1       |      2      |   3    |
| Flower   | amaryllis | bellflower | iris |
| Color           | blood-red         | amber         | mauve |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-4-8::.
