There are 3 different nationalities: american, japanese, australian
1. the american is between the japanese and the person drinking mirinda##2
2. the australian is in an odd position##4
3. the japanese is on the left of the person drinking sprite##1

.:: Answer ::.
|        |   1    |  2   |     3     |
| Beverage   | 7up | sprite | mirinda |
| Nationality    | japanese    | american | australian     |

