.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-4-9::.
City: san-francisco, rome, venice
House: craftsman, modern, farmhouse
1. the farmhouse house is in an odd position##4
2. the modern house is on the left of the person traveling to san-francisco##1
3. the farmhouse house is on the left of the person traveling to rome##1
4. the farmhouse house is on the left or right of the modern house##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |    2     |    3     |
| City   | venice   | rome  | san-francisco  |
| House         | farmhouse | modern | craftsman |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-4-10::.
3 different brands of cigars are smoked: montecristo, tiparillo, ritmeester
The people prefer 3 different types of sport: water-polo, swimming, parkour
1. the person who's sport is water-polo is on the right of the ritmeester-smoker##1
2. the person who's sport is parkour is in an even position##4
3. the person who's sport is parkour is on the right of the montecristo-smoker##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |   1    |     2     |   3    |
| Cigar   | montecristo    | ritmeester      | tiparillo |
| Sport       | swimming | parkour | water-polo   |

