.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-4-11::.
The people grow 3 different varities of flowers: poppy, marigold, begonia
3 different games are played: chess, monopoly, whist
1. the person who growsbegonia is on the right of the person who growsmarigold##1
2. the person playing chess is the person who growspoppy##1
3. the person playing whist is the person who growsbegonia##1
4. the person who growsbegonia is in an even position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|             |   1    |    2    |     3      |
| Flower         | marigold | begonia | poppy |
| Game   | monopoly | whist   | chess |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-4-12::.
House: wooden, tower, art-deco
There are 3 different favourite colors: coral, chestnut, grey
1. the person who likes grey is on the right of the person who likes coral##1
2. the wooden house is the person who likes grey##1
3. the person who likes chestnut is on the left or right of the tower house##3
4. the person who likes grey is in an odd position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |     2     |     3      |
| House   | art-deco | tower | wooden |
| Color     | chestnut     | coral   | grey        |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-4-13::.
3 different brands of cigars are smoked: aristoff, bolivar, blend
3 different pets are kept: snake, rabbit, pony
1. the owner of the pony is on the right of the blend-smoker##1
2. the owner of the snake is the bolivar-smoker##1
3. the blend-smoker is in an odd position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |    2     |    3    |
| Cigar   | blend  | aristoff | bolivar   |
| Pet         | rabbit | pony   | snake |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-4-14::.
House: townhouse, palace, farmhouse
3 different games are played: scrabble, mah-jongg, monopoly
1. the farmhouse house is between the palace house and the person playing mah-jongg##2
2. the palace house is in an odd position##4
3. the person playing mah-jongg is on the far left or far right##3
4. the farmhouse house is on the right of the person playing scrabble##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |      1      |    2    |   3    |
| House   | palace | farmhouse | townhouse |
| Game     | scrabble    | monopoly  | mah-jongg   |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-4-15::.
The people use 3 different means of transport: subway, helicopter, motorbike
The people have 3 different hobbies: filmmaking, board-games, photography
1. the person driving the motorbike is on the right of the person driving the subway##1
2. the person who's hobby is board-games is on the left of the person who's hobby is filmmaking##1
3. the person who's hobby is board-games is on the left or right of the person driving the motorbike##3
4. the person driving the motorbike is in an even position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |    2    |    3    |
| Transport   | subway  | motorbike     | helicopter |
| Hobby   | board-games | filmmaking | photography    |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-4-16::.
The people prefer 3 different types of sport: basketball, swimming, skateboarding
The people use 3 different means of transport: airplane, ship, taxi
1. the person driving the taxi is the person who's sport is skateboarding##1
2. the person driving the taxi is on the left of the person who's sport is basketball##1
3. the person driving the ship is in an odd position##4
4. the person driving the airplane is on the left or right of the person driving the ship##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |    2     |   3   |
| Sport          | skateboarding | basketball | swimming  |
| Transport   | taxi      | airplane  | ship |

