.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-4-18::.
3 different brands of cigars are smoked: oliveros, davidoff, bluemaster
The people prefer 3 different types of sport: parkour, weightlifting, baseball
1. the person who's sport is baseball is on the right of the oliveros-smoker##1
2. the oliveros-smoker is in the middle##1
3. the bluemaster-smoker is the person who's sport is weightlifting##1
4. the person who's sport is parkour is in an even position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |     2     |     3     |
| Cigar         | bluemaster | oliveros   | davidoff |
| Sport   | weightlifting   | parkour | baseball      |

