.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-4-19::.
3 different games are played: backgammon, scrabble, canasta
There are 3 different favourite colors: azure, light-blue, grey
1. the person who likes grey is on the left or right of the person playing backgammon##3
2. the person playing backgammon is in an odd position##4
3. the person playing canasta is on the right of the person playing scrabble##1
4. the person playing scrabble is on the left of the person who likes azure##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |       2       |    3     |
| Game      | backgammon | scrabble | canasta |
| Color   | light-blue   | grey          | azure |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-4-20::.
3 different games are played: scrabble, snooker, whist
3 different brands of cigars are smoked: aristoff, vegafina, siglo
1. the siglo-smoker is in an odd position##4
2. the siglo-smoker is on the left of the person playing whist##1
3. the person playing whist is in an even position##4
4. the vegafina-smoker is on the right of the person playing snooker##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |    1     |    2     |     3      |
| Game     | snooker  | whist   | scrabble |
| Cigar   | siglo | vegafina | aristoff       |

 